# =============================================================================
# MenuLink · top-level .gitignore
# =============================================================================

# --- Secrets ---
# Never commit .env*.local — contains Supabase service_role and anon keys
.env
.env.local
.env.*.local
**/.env.local
**/.env.*.local

# --- Node / Next.js ---
node_modules/
**/node_modules/
.next/
**/.next/
out/
**/out/
*.tsbuildinfo
**/*.tsbuildinfo
next-env.d.ts
**/next-env.d.ts

# --- Supabase CLI ---
**/supabase/.branches/
**/supabase/.temp/
**/supabase/.env

# --- Graphify outputs (regenerable) ---
**/graphify-out/
.graphify_*

# --- Obsidian vault config (per-user editor state, not project content) ---
.obsidian/

# --- OS noise ---
.DS_Store
**/.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
**/Thumbs.db
desktop.ini
**/desktop.ini

# --- Editor noise ---
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
*.swo
*~

# --- Logs ---
*.log
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*
pnpm-debug.log*

# --- Build artifacts ---
dist/
build/
*.tgz

# --- Client raw photo library (460 MB source dump — photos live in Supabase Storage) ---
docs/clients/ITEMS_PHOTO/
# --- Client working photo dirs (local image-tooling output; not committed) ---
docs/clients/Design-template/
docs/clients/almosafer/new-photos/
# --- Coffee Secret client raw data (POS financial xlsx, logo, working screenshots — photos live in Supabase Storage) ---
docs/clients/coffe-secret/
# --- Generated photo catalog (visual xlsx w/ embedded thumbnails — regenerate via scripts/catalog/build-photo-catalog.mjs) ---
.claude/skills/menulink-photo-catalog/data/*.xlsx

# --- Office temp lock files ---
**/~$*

# --- Repo cleanup Phase 1 (regenerable graph output, secret quarantine, typo/junk dirs) ---
/secrets-quarantine/
/.graph/
docs/pormpts/
docs/screenshots-tsests/

# --- Phase 1.5: keep KNOWN dev credentials off the `git add -A` surface ---
# These untracked trees/doc carry documented dev creds (SQL sa-login, linked-server
# login, POS PIN, web passwords). Redacting the runnable operate scripts would break
# them, so ignore now; un-ignore + redact prose + keep scripts local-only in Phase 2/3.
/.claude/skills/punnelifosys-pos/
/.claude/skills/punnelifosys-pos-operate/
/.claude/skills/punnelifosys-feature-dev/
/docs/REPO-CLEANUP-PLAN.md

# --- Installed generic skill trees (marketplace-installed, not MenuLink-owned; regenerable) ---
/.claude/skills/brand-design-md/
/.claude/skills/brand/
/.claude/skills/design-system/
/.claude/skills/slides/
/.claude/skills/ui-styling/
/.claude/skills/ui-ux-pro-max/
